<p class="text-center">This story is about a person who experiences burnout. At the end of the story there are links for tips on how to recognize burnout, what it is, how to prevent it, how to recover from burnout and self care tips.</p>
<p class="text-center">The purpose of this story is to bring awareness on burnout and how society brushes over this topic. Many people experience burnout and sometimes do not even know about burnout until they are experiencing it. My hope is to bring awareness on this topic in order to hopefully have people realize that it is okay to take it slow and take your time unlike how social media presents time(such as how you should supposedly should be acomplishing things at a certain time in your life, which is not always realistic). By seeing burnout in this story, my goal is to have the reader think about their own mental health and take action in practing self care. </p>
